I am using VE SDK build I20050713.

We can't reproduce this. Was this in a new clean workspace after you installed
the VE driver? Or was it an older workspace?

If it was an older workspace, then bring up a VE editor and then close it, then
do Projects->Clean...->Clean all projects. And wait for the build to complete.

There may of been some stale cache information since cache format was changing a
lot.

Since we can't reproduce, I'm closing the defect. If you can reproduce this,
please reopen the defect. Thanks.

My apologies, just noticed that in the defect I entered that I left out the 
fact that I was typing in a class name that could not resolve.
